---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/en/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/en/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Caveduke" description="Caveduke privacy policy. Information about personal data processing in accordance with the GDPR." lang="en">
	<Navbar />
	
	<main class="bg-[var(--color-noir)] pt-40 pb-24 px-6 md:px-12">
		<article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose-legal">
			
			<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
				<div class="w-8 h-px bg-[var(--color-gold)]"></div>
				<p class="font-accent text-[var(--color-gold)] tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">Legal</p>
			</div>

			<h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] leading-tight mb-6">
				Privacy <span class="italic text-[var(--color-gold)]">Policy</span>
			</h1>

			<p class="font-body text-sm text-[var(--color-silver)]/50 mb-12">Last updated: February 27, 2026</p>

			<div class="space-y-10 font-body text-[var(--color-silver)]/80 text-base leading-relaxed">

				<!-- 1. Data Controller -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
					<ul class="space-y-1 list-none pl-0">
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Identity:</strong> Caveduke, S.L.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Tax ID:</strong> [Company Tax ID]</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Registered address:</strong> C/ Juan Ramón Jiménez, 34, 08100 Mollet del Vallés (Barcelona), Spain</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:caveduke@caveduke.com" class="text-[var(--color-gold)] hover:underline">caveduke@caveduke.com</a></li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Phone:</strong> (+34) 697 182 482</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- 2. Data Collected -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">2. Personal Data We Collect</h2>
					<p>Through our website, we may collect the following personal data:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li>Full name</li>
						<li>Email address</li>
						<li>Phone number</li>
						<li>Postal address (when required for quotes or deliveries)</li>
						<li>Browsing data (cookies, IP address, browser type)</li>
						<li>Any additional information voluntarily provided through our contact forms</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- 3. Purpose -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">3. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
					<p>The personal data you provide will be processed for the following purposes:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li>Managing contact requests, enquiries and quotes</li>
						<li>Sending commercial information about our products and services, with prior explicit consent</li>
						<li>Managing the commercial relationship with clients</li>
						<li>Complying with applicable legal obligations</li>
						<li>Improving user experience on our website</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- 4. Legal Basis -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
					<p>The processing of your personal data is based on:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Consent</strong> (Art. 6.1.a GDPR): when submitting contact forms or requesting information.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Performance of a contract</strong> (Art. 6.1.b GDPR): for managing orders and quotes.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Legitimate interest</strong> (Art. 6.1.f GDPR): to improve our services and user experience.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Legal obligation</strong> (Art. 6.1.c GDPR): to comply with tax and commercial obligations.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- 5. Data Retention -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
					<p>Personal data will be retained for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose for which it was collected and to determine any liabilities arising from that purpose. Specifically:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li>Client data: for the duration of the contractual relationship and, once terminated, for the applicable legal limitation periods.</li>
						<li>Contact and enquiry data: for a maximum of 2 years from the last interaction.</li>
						<li>Marketing communications data: until the data subject withdraws consent.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- 6. Recipients -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">6. Data Recipients</h2>
					<p>Personal data will not be disclosed to third parties except where required by law. The following may have access to your data:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li>Technology service providers (web hosting, email services)</li>
						<li>Public authorities where legally required</li>
						<li>Financial institutions for payment management</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- 7. Rights -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
					<p>In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Access:</strong> request information about the personal data we process.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Rectification:</strong> request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Erasure:</strong> request deletion of your data when no longer necessary.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Restriction:</strong> request restriction of processing under certain circumstances.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Portability:</strong> receive your data in a structured, commonly used format.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Objection:</strong> object to the processing of your data on legitimate grounds.</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="mt-4">To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:caveduke@caveduke.com" class="text-[var(--color-gold)] hover:underline">caveduke@caveduke.com</a> or at our postal address, enclosing a copy of your identity document.</p>
					<p class="mt-3">You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the <strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD)</strong> at <a href="https://www.aepd.es" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-gold)] hover:underline">www.aepd.es</a>, or with your local supervisory authority.</p>
				</section>

				<!-- 8. Cookies -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">8. Cookie Policy</h2>
					<p>Our website uses first-party and third-party cookies for the following purposes:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Technical cookies:</strong> necessary for the website to function properly.</li>
						<li><strong class="text-[var(--color-ivory)]">Analytical cookies:</strong> to collect anonymous statistics about website usage.</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="mt-3">You may configure your browser to reject cookies, although doing so may affect the functionality of certain sections of the website.</p>
				</section>

				<!-- 9. Security -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">9. Security Measures</h2>
					<p>We have implemented the necessary technical and organisational measures to ensure the security of personal data and prevent its alteration, loss, unauthorised processing or access, in accordance with the state of the art, the nature of the data stored and the risks to which it is exposed.</p>
				</section>

				<!-- 10. Changes -->
				<section>
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">10. Changes to this Policy</h2>
					<p>Caveduke reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy to adapt it to legislative or case-law developments, as well as industry practices. Any changes will be announced on this page with reasonable advance notice before implementation.</p>
				</section>

				<!-- Legislation -->
				<section class="border-t border-[var(--color-silver)]/10 pt-8 mt-12">
					<h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[var(--color-ivory)] mb-4">Applicable Legislation</h2>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-sm">
						<li>Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council (GDPR)</li>
						<li>Spanish Organic Law 3/2018, of 5 December, on the Protection of Personal Data and Guarantee of Digital Rights (LOPD-GDD)</li>
						<li>Spanish Law 34/2002, of 11 July, on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI-CE)</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

			</div>
		</article>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</BaseLayout>
